{"id":861,"date":"2025-04-04T04:42:33","date_gmt":"2025-04-04T04:42:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/swiftbeulah.co.ke\/?p=861"},"modified":"2025-04-22T06:15:12","modified_gmt":"2025-04-22T06:15:12","slug":"protecting-partnership-businesses-disruption-caused-by-death","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/swiftbeulah.co.ke\/2025\/04\/04\/protecting-partnership-businesses-disruption-caused-by-death\/","title":{"rendered":"PROTECTING PARTNERSHIP BUSINESSES DISRUPTION CAUSED BY DEATH."},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">As business partners come together with purpose of doing business together , they start with the end in their minds .<\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Among the many things that they discuss and agree on how to face is death  of either of  them .<\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This because loss of a life results to business disruption  but can be protected with a partners life insurance cover .<\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This game changer cushion helps in the following ways :<\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">1.Ensures the surviving partner has the funds to buy  off the shares of the deceased,<\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">2.Covers any outstanding debts so the living is not left with outstanding liabilities<\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">3.Guarantees smooth ownership transition .<\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Always consider the partners life cover cause life happens .<\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>As business partners come together with purpose of doing business together , they start with the end in their minds . Among the many things that they discuss and agree [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":704,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","stic